  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mies, M-I-E-S; van, V-A-N; der, D-E-R; Rohe, R-O-H-E.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he got these commissions-- her husband got these commissions in America in the early '30s or mid-30s, I believe.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then his, his name became, became very well-known here and had a very good, lucrative practice.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they, they were separated, basically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He stayed here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she stayed there because the girls-- they had three daughters who were in school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she couldn't just up and go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And besides, there were other considerations as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were very anti-Nazi.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if there are any good Germans-- which I have many times in my life doubted-- these would certainly belong to them, and she particularly.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She hid my parents, at, of course, obvious cost and risk to her life and liberty and family for several months, it seems, and-- several weeks at least.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know the exact time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And from there, they had arranged certain stops before they got to the border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They must have had false papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I don't know the, the details of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But they got to the border all right.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had these different stops.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The border was near Innsbruck-- Swiss border, border between Germany, or rather, Austria-- which was part of Germany at that time-- and, and Switzerland in an area called the Vorarlberg.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's the, the Swiss name for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "V-O-R-A-R-L-B-E-R-G, which is not far from Innsbruck, which is a major [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Austrian town in the-- in the Alps. not in the Alps, near, near the Alps, very hilly country.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
